In contrast, trying to turn the Symbol into a string implicitly, like with [`Array.prototype.join`](https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-array.prototype.join), (or `Array.prototype.toString`, which internally calls `Array.prototype.join`, or `+`, etc), invokes the [ToString](https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-tostring) operation, which throws when the argument is a Symbol.

